[Panting]
We made it.

01:20:02.180 --> 01:20:06.476
It worked.
[Chuckling] It worked.

01:20:06.601 --> 01:20:09.812
-Wait. Get down!
-Ouch. Ow.

01:20:09.896 --> 01:20:12.273
