-[Sighs]

01:21:50.455 --> 01:21:52.373
Partner.

01:21:55.501 --> 01:21:57.837
Partner.

01:21:57.920 --> 01:22:00.965
Hey, guys, come on!

01:22:01.090 --> 01:22:03.009
You don't wanna stay here
forever, do you?

01:22:03.092 --> 01:22:06.929
